        .. contents ::
        
        Summary
        =======
        
        HTTP-related tools to adapt WSGI for the flows methodoloy
        
        Since it is really just a dependency of a Flows it probably
        isn't much use as a standalone package yet.
        
        
        Get Started
        ===========
        
        * Download and install from source
        
        Author
        ======
        
        `James Gardner <http://jimmyg.org/>`_
        
        
